title: WiFi Password Decryptor 3.3 Portable
description:
WiFi Password Decryptor 3.3 Portable | 5 Mb

WiFi Password Decryptor is a useful software to instantly recover Wireless account passwords stored on your system.It automatically recovers all type of Wireless Keys/Passwords (WEP/WPA/WPA2 etc) stored by Windows Wireless Configuration Manager.

WiFi Password Decryptor reveals WiFi passwords hidden under asterisks, which are stored in the Windows Wireless Configuration Manger panel. It comes in handy if you have lost or forgotten the password that prevents you from connecting to the Internet.

Users should not misunderstand the tool's purpose, as it cannot crack passwords over a wireless network, as the name might imply
